data.description: Welcome home! Where you'll find a property that blends comfort, privacy, and endless possibilities on its expansive 6-acre plot of flat valuable land. This charming house offers an idyllic retreat from the hustle and bustle of city life. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home offers comfortable living spaces for you and your loved ones. The primary bedroom features two walk-in closets, and an en-suite bathroom that is quipped with a jacuzzi tub, walk in shower, and dual vanity sinks. The kitchen is spacious and well-appointed, allowing for easy meal preparation and entertaining. Custom cabinets in the laundry room provide additional storage options. Additional features include a 12x24 wooden shed and a 48x30 steel building that can accommodate tractors, campers, and more. Whether you're looking to enjoy the serenity of the surrounding nature or need space for your hobbies, this property has it all. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! Showings start 11/28!
